        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">Marval has not been identified.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The Kalmuck and Khirgis peoples (now Kalmyk and Kazakh) lived in what are now the Republics of Kalmykia and Kazakhstan. Tarentula is an alternative spelling of tarantula. CD does not discuss tarantulas his published works.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">Marval probably refers to kibitkas, felt and leather tents used by nomadic Kalmyk families (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_5166.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Maksimov 2008</ref>, p. 114).</note>
        </div>        
            
